'''飓风埃拉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Ella}}）是有纪录以来加拿大海域出现过的最强飓风，于1978年8月30日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]南侧形成，然后在向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]移动期间迅速增强。9月1日，埃拉的风速已提升到每小时205公里，预计会在繁忙的[[劳动节_(美国)|劳动节]]期间从[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]附近经过。风暴接下来约24小时几乎停止移动，然后转向东北远离海岸。9月4日，埃拉在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]近海达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的四级飓风标准，然后逐渐减弱并从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南洋面经过，最终被大规模[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]吸收。

即将到来的节日令大量人流涌入北卡罗莱纳州，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]向该州发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]。此举导致旅游业受到重创，但外滩群岛沿岸没有出现极端恶劣天气。气旋激起大浪并引发轻度[[海蚀|海滩侵蚀]]，但没有造成人员伤亡或任何破坏。飓风经过纽芬兰岛时最强风力位于中心东侧和南面，所以加拿大没有遭受严重破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Ella 1978 track.png|left}}
1978年8月下旬，一股大规模[[冷锋|冷锋]]在西[[大西洋|大西洋]]几乎停止移动，然后逐渐消散，于8月28日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南海域催生出[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]。形成环流后，系统于8月30日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南偏南方向约840公里洋面发展成热带低气压。受北侧的[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]影响，气旋稳步向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，附近船只的观测纪录表明热带低气压成形18小时后就达到热带风暴标准。<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Miles B. Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 1978 | title = Hurricane Ella Preliminary Report | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183256/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/prenhc/ | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/prenhc/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月30日晚22点，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始针对风暴发布公告<ref>{{cite web | author = Frank | date = 1978-08-30 | title = Tropical Depression Advisory | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | format = [[JPEG|JPG]] | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024051017/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub302200z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub302200z.jpg }}</ref>。仅三小时后，气旋呈现急剧强化趋势，因此升级成热带风暴并获名“埃拉”（{{lang|en|Ella}}）<ref>{{cite web | author = Hebert | date = 1978-08-30 | title = Tropical Storm Ella Special Advisory One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223401/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub310100z.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | accessdate = 2010-03-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub310100z.jpg }}</ref>。

风暴迅速增强，附近船只及[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机的观测数据表明埃拉于8月31日晚成为飓风<ref name="tcr" />。气象机构此时预计气旋会转向东北，不会[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]，还认为风暴会在繁忙的[[劳动节_(美国)|劳动节]]期间从距陆地不到85公里近海经过<ref>{{cite web | author = Miles Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-08-31 | title = Hurricane Ella Discussion | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173256/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd3121z.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd3121z.jpg }}</ref>。9月1日，埃拉达到第一波强度高峰，持续风速为每小时205公里，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属三级飓风标准，成为大型飓风。与此同时，有[[低压槽|短波槽]]抵达[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]，促使埃拉放缓移动速度并略朝北面转向，短波槽后方的[[高压脊|高压脊]]还令风暴几乎停止移动24小时。<ref name="tcr" />在这24小时里，风暴不再对北卡罗莱纳州构成影响，对流迅速消亡，风速也随之下降<ref>{{cite web | author = Pelissier | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-02 | title = Hurricane Ella Discussion | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170203/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0209z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0209z.jpg }}</ref>。

9月3日，受美国东岸另一个低压槽影响，气旋加速朝东北移动，经过已经消亡的高压脊<ref name="tcr" />。此时埃拉的持续风速已降至每小时180公里<ref name="tcr" />，但气象部门预计接下来受[[斜压|斜压不稳]]影响，飓风强度不会再有大幅下降<ref>{{cite web | author = Pelissier | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170939/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0309z.jpg | title = Hurricane Ella Discussion | accessdate = 2010-03-28 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0309z.jpg | format = JPG }}</ref>。埃拉没有再继续减弱，而是开始显著增强。9月4日清晨，风暴再度成为大型飓风，飓风猎人证实气旋于当天在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]][[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]以南约540公里洋面达到风力时速220公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。埃拉由此成为有纪录以来加拿大海域的最强飓风<ref name="Canada">{{cite web | author = Canadian Hurricane Centre | date = 2010-09-14 | title = 1978-Ella | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | archivedate = 2016-11-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161120191722/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=DB671096-1 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=DB671096-1 }}</ref>。达到最高强度后，飓风马上就因行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]降低而开始减弱<ref name="tcr" />。9月5日，风暴从[[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）附近掠过，最强风力位于中心南面及东侧<ref name="a24">{{cite web | author = John Hope | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-05 | title = Hurricane Ella Advisory 24 | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170608/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub050400z.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub050400z.jpg }}</ref>。[[对流|对流]]完全从中心剥离<ref>{{cite web | author = Miles Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-05 | title = Hurricane Ella Discussion | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182056/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0509z.jpg | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/tropdisc/tcd0509z.jpg }}</ref>，飓风随即转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]并由更大规模的中纬度天气系统吸收<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Ella_(1978).JPG|right]]

9月1日埃拉达到第一波强度高峰之际，美国国家飓风中心预计风暴会在繁忙的劳动节期间逼近北卡罗莱纳州海岸，因此向[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]<ref name="tcr" />。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）办事处要求可能受气旋影响地区的电视台和广播电台在常规报导基础上加播风暴公告信息，及时把最新动向告知当地居民<ref>{{cite web | author = A.J. Hull | date = 1978-09-01 | title = Special Request to East North Carolina and Southeast Virginia | publisher = Cape Hatteras National Weather Service | accessdate = 2017-02-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat012050z.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat012050z.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG }}</ref>。此外，哈特拉斯角办事处还发出公告，建议小型船只留在港口不要出海，提醒居民“保持警惕，不要听信流言”<ref>{{cite web | author = Cape Hatteras National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1978-09-01 | title = Hurricane Ella Local Statement Number 3 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024030735/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat012230z.jpg | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat012230z.jpg }}</ref>。面对风暴威胁，只能通过轮渡前往的[[奥克拉科克_(北卡罗莱纳州)|奥克拉科克岛]]（{{lang|en|Ocracoke Island}}）和[[了望角|了望角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Lookout}}）将露营地暂时关闭，减少气旋来袭期间留在当地的人口<ref>{{cite web | author = Cape Hatteras National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1978-09-02 | title = Hurricane Ella Local Statement Number 6 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat020730z.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat020730z.jpg }}</ref>。

实际情况表明，整场飓风自始至终远离海岸<ref name="tcr" />，暴雨和雷暴区距海岸线最近时都还有85公里<ref>{{cite web | author = Cape Hatteras National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1978-09-02 | title = Hurricane Ella Local Statement Number 10 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190606/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat021900z.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat021900z.jpg }}</ref>。埃拉一度几乎停止移动，在此期间产生二至三米高的大浪，海岸沿线还出现[[离岸流|离岸流]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Cape Hatteras National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1978-09-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190730/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat022230z.jpg | title = Hurricane Ella Local Statement Number 12 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/local/hat022230z.jpg | format = JPG | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。气旋在[[钻石浅滩灯塔|钻石浅滩灯塔]]（{{lang|en|Diamond Shoal Light}}）产生时速50公里的阵风，比其他地点都高。大部分海滩的沙丘都受到海浪冲刷<ref name="nc">{{cite web | author = A. J. Hull | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1978-09-07 | title = Preliminary Report on Hurricane Ella | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230654/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/preloc/hat07.01.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/preloc/hat07.01.jpg }}</ref>，部分海滩受到轻度[[海蚀|侵蚀]]，流失的沙子在数天后恢复<ref>{{cite web | author = Albert R. Hinn | publisher = Wilmington National Weather Service | date = 1978-09-07 | title = Information for Hurricane Ella Survey Report | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/postevent/hinn07.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220720/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/postevent/hinn07.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG }}</ref>。虽然风暴一度逼近更北面的[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]，但该州海岸沿线没有出现大浪<ref>{{cite web | author = Terry Ritter | publisher = Norfolk National Weather Service | date = 1978-09-06 | title = Storm Report, Hurricane Ella | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192850/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/preloc/orf06.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/preloc/orf06.jpg }}</ref>。

最终风暴最重大的影响是旅游业遭受重创<ref name="tcr" />。通常情况下，劳动节是美国夏季旅游业的最后一波高峰期，许多人都会选择前往外滩群岛度假。但由于气象机构发布飓风观察预警，当地无论交通客流量还是包括酒店在内的各行各业营收都大幅下降。美国国家气象局的气象学家表示，之所以发布飓风观察预警是因为外滩群岛仅有一条道路进出，不能等到最后时刻才来疏散成千上万的游客<ref>{{cite web | author = Coastland Times | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-07 | title = News Clippings about Hurricane Ella | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230102/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/news/ct0907.01.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/news/ct0907.01.jpg }}</ref>。这位气象学家还称，风暴期间会发布级别低于飓风观察预警的警报<ref name="nc" />。

经过加拿大海域期间，埃拉的最强风力位于中心以南和以东，所以该国没有受到严重影响<ref name="a24" />。气旋来袭前，纽芬兰岛天气预报办事处向该岛东南部发布飓风警告<ref>{{cite web | author = Gilbert Clark | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1978-09-04 | title = Hurricane Ella Advisory 22 | accessdate = 2017-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170348/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub041600z.jpg | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0076-jpg/1978/atlantic/ella/public/pub041600z.jpg }}</ref>。新斯科舍和纽芬兰岛间的轮渡服务受到影响，船只返回港口躲避。降雨量相对很少，最高的纽芬兰岛东南部也只有约61毫米，持续风速则以开普雷斯最高，达到115公里。<ref name="Canada" />

